{"tid":523872,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"甸恩承認錯判12碼累雲加停賽","createTime":"2018-01-09T04:15:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-09T14:41:44.000Z","uid":31314,"like":3,"dislike":25,"uniUserReply":57,"replies":[{"pid":"986b3beafc28d2dff80c19bad5832476c023fd6d","tid":523872,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T04:15:01.000Z","msg":"英超球證公會常務經理拉利指，球證甸恩承認自己在阿仙奴對西布朗的英超，判錯了12碼，令兵工廠失去2分。  <br />\n<br />\n阿仙奴在早前的英超作客西布朗，完場前中堅哥林張伯斯禁區內「波打手」，球證甸恩（Mike Dean）爭議性地判了12碼，結果前鋒積洛迪古斯射入，助主隊逼和兵工廠1:1。  <br />\n<br />\n「我知道甸恩要是有機會，會希望推翻那個判決。他是一名非常誠實的人，傳訊息予我們說自己判錯了。」拉利（Mike Riley）指，他也認為不應該判罰12碼，要是英超有VAR視像裁判技術，將可以避免這種情況再次發生。  <br />\n<br />\n不過，甸恩認錯也幫不了阿仙奴或領隊雲加。因為雲加在該仗賽後，對傳媒公開批評甸恩的12碼判決，據指更親自到球證室表態，結果被英格蘭足總判罰停賽3場，並罰款4萬鎊。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.telegraph.co.uk/content/dam/football/2017/12/31/TELEMMGLPICT000150213783_trans_NvBQzQNjv4Bq9ipoqzrpJx-0lCLDc3i7WuNWTgnqJQdkHh6JBY3TaR4.jpeg?imwidth=480\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.telegraph.co.uk%2Fcontent%2Fdam%2Ffootball%2F2017%2F12%2F31%2FTELEMMGLPICT000150213783_trans_NvBQzQNjv4Bq9ipoqzrpJx-0lCLDc3i7WuNWTgnqJQdkHh6JBY3TaR4.jpeg%3Fimwidth%3D480&h=95b6c395&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.independent.co.uk/s3fs-public/styles/article_small/public/thumbnails/image/2018/01/08/08/arsene-wenger-mike-dean.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.independent.co.uk%2Fs3fs-public%2Fstyles%2Farticle_small%2Fpublic%2Fthumbnails%2Fimage%2F2018%2F01%2F08%2F08%2Farsene-wenger-mike-dean.jpg&h=a28118e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.completesportsnigeria.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/IMG_20180104_000235-600x400.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.completesportsnigeria.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F01%2FIMG_20180104_000235-600x400.jpg&h=a452f9a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.dailymail.co.uk/i/pix/2018/01/05/15/47A9BE3700000578-5239443-image-a-92_1515167835721.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2Fi%2Fpix%2F2018%2F01%2F05%2F15%2F47A9BE3700000578-5239443-image-a-92_1515167835721.jpg&h=0fd93cd3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c0fa6df1142365092fc36cc5a28af7ecf9f508a5","tid":523872,"uid":60959,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T04:18:00.000Z","msg":"好撚荒謬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb1cd5a898a32092a8681c8187295896815ae2da","tid":523872,"uid":8968,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T04:18:05.000Z","msg":"迫害<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4eeedb6a43fdd8bba26391d549b80d335129fab4","tid":523872,"uid":11254,"like":29,"dislike":1,"score":28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T04:18:45.000Z","msg":"熱狗可以吹阿狗比賽已經夠ON9喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7edd14008fe08babf16169d6b2d3dd0ef6860fed","tid":523872,"uid":61271,"like":23,"dislike":1,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T04:20:09.000Z","msg":"出名執法水平低都仲可以繼續做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另一方面，科技先進有VAR，又話拖慢比賽進度 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73e1324f3c6075724aacefbd4909a7149f36e54a","tid":523872,"uid":50385,"like":23,"dislike":1,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T04:20:23.000Z","msg":"累鳩埋我輸錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 拍下蘿友道個歉又當無事發生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82c5d64a081293e024d4a6ab71f301b9a1bd0bff","tid":523872,"uid":4957,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T04:20:34.000Z","msg":"天滅雲加"},{"pid":"b1027a87926599ef9a0dcbd3c492336d45cfecd1","tid":523872,"uid":31314,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"73e1324f3c6075724aacefbd4909a7149f36e54a","tid":523872,"uid":50