Dc3i7WuNWTgnqJQdkHh6JBY3TaR4.jpeg%3Fimwidth%3D480&h=95b6c395&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.independent.co.uk/s3fs-public/styles/article_small/public/thumbnails/image/2018/01/08/08/arsene-wenger-mike-dean.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.independent.co.uk%2Fs3fs-public%2Fstyles%2Farticle_small%2Fpublic%2Fthumbnails%2Fimage%2F2018%2F01%2F08%2F08%2Farsene-wenger-mike-dean.jpg&h=a28118e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.completesportsnigeria.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/IMG_20180104_000235-600x400.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.completesportsnigeria.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F01%2FIMG_20180104_000235-600x400.jpg&h=a452f9a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.dailymail.co.uk/i/pix/2018/01/05/15/47A9BE3700000578-5239443-image-a-92_1515167835721.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2Fi%2Fpix%2F2018%2F01%2F05%2F15%2F47A9BE3700000578-5239443-image-a-92_1515167835721.jpg&h=0fd93cd3&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n雲加型到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebd20f8b7fa0d9649794ff1fc5e33d421bf44c5b","tid":523872,"uid":3813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T06:07:31.000Z","msg":"到底件灰色冷衫有冇鈕"},{"pid":"4e5f5aebb9f4500397234bcab29cbfcd81f02d60","tid":523872,"uid":30478,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"2191a3b09b66ec58cfc0482114c5f59077e4269d","tid":523872,"uid":46892,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T06:02:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>英超球證公會常務經理拉利指，球證甸恩承認自己在阿仙奴對西布朗的英超，判錯了12碼，令兵工廠失去2分。  <br />\n<br />\n阿仙奴在早前的英超作客西布朗，完場前中堅哥林張伯斯禁區內「波打手」，球證甸恩（Mike Dean）爭議性地判了12碼，結果前鋒積洛迪古斯射入，助主隊逼和兵工廠1:1。  <br />\n<br />\n「我知道甸恩要是有機會，會希望推翻那個判決。他是一名非常誠實的人，傳訊息予我們說自己判錯了。」拉利（Mike Riley）指，他也認為不應該判罰12碼，要是英超有VAR視像裁判技術，將可以避免這種情況再次發生。  <br />\n<br />\n不過，甸恩認錯也幫不了阿仙奴或領隊雲加。因為雲加在該仗賽後，對傳媒公開批評甸恩的12碼判決，據指更親自到球證室表態，結果被英格蘭足總判罰停賽